            "title": "兌換英鎊🇬🇧點先最抵？比較銀行找換店最新兌換價",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"兌換英鎊｜英鎊匯價波動，我們今日就比較多間外幣找換店及各大銀行的兌換價，以及列出多間找換店及銀行的匯價連結，給大家參考！此外，更新增部分銀行兌換外幣高息定存優惠，兌換英鎊高息定存息率高達17厘！\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"696\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/oyElZ.YhIJkm4G_NyeDEBA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY5Ng--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-images/2020-01/157218c0-3074-11ea-bcfd-b86854a99a41\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">兌換英鎊｜英鎊匯價波動，我們今日就比較多間外幣找換店及各大銀行的兌換價，以及列出多間找換店及銀行的匯價連結，給大家參考！此外，更新增部分銀行兌換外幣高息定存優惠，兌換英鎊高息定存息率高達17厘！</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">英鎊匯價波動，我們今日就比較多間外幣找換店及各大銀行的兌換價，以及列出多間找換店及銀行的匯價連結，給大家參考！此外，更新增部分銀行兌換外幣高息定存優惠，兌換英鎊高息定存息率高達17厘！</p><hr class=\"my-module-gap border-dirty-seagull border-x-1\"/><blockquote class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull\" style=\"padding-bottom:min(300px, undefined%)\"></div></blockquote><hr class=\"my-module-gap border-dirty-seagull border-x-1\"/><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">英鎊兌美元周五於亞洲交易時段表現牛皮。匯價早前自1.3445的本周低位輕微反彈，整體走勢仍然偏軟，市場入市態度審慎。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">市場焦點落在貨幣政策走向。英倫銀行行長貝利日前在國會財政委員會作供時表示，若通脹按預期回落至2%目標水平，當局有減息空間。言論被市場視為偏鴿，帶動對英國年內減息的預期升溫，英鎊因而受壓。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-3e3dc280-c97e-4d81-bbc7-d7aa2dc44b7f-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">反觀美國方面，聯儲局1月議息會議紀錄顯示，官員對進一步減息態度審慎，並不急於行動，甚至討論若通脹未見明顯放緩，或需重新考慮加息可能。相關取向令市場削減對美國大幅放寬政策的押注，美元靠穩於月內高位附近，限制英鎊反彈。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">展望後市，英國未有重要經濟數據公布，投資者將留意英倫銀行首席經濟師Huw Pill的講話；美國稍後公布生產者物價指數（PPI），或為匯市帶來新啟示。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>延伸閱讀：</strong></p><ul class=\"mb-module-gap\"><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link yahoo-link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:英倫銀行行長貝利:3月會否減息仍是未知數;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas;outcm:mb_qualified_link;_E:mb_qualified_link;ct:story;\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/%E8%8B%B1%E5%80%AB%E9%8A%80%E8%A1%8C%E8%A1%8C%E9%95%B7%E8%B2%9D%E5%88%A9-3%E6%9C%88%E6%9C%83%E5%90%A6%E6%B8%9B%E6%81%AF%E4%BB%8D%E6%98%AF%E6%9C%AA%E7%9F%A5%E6%95%B8-000118185.html\"><strong>英倫銀行行長貝利:3月會否減息仍是未知數</strong></a></p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link yahoo-link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:2;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:英鎊今日走勢:央行決策者作證期間英鎊小幅走低;cpos:2;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas;outcm:mb_qualified_link;_E:mb_qualified_link;ct:story;\" href=\"https://hk.f